{"id": "1513760393271443487", "channel_id": "1513760393271443487", "author_id": "1355724968956002314", "author_name": "xyakoto", "content": "These 3 numbers heavily impact a team's HP and relic damages.\nBut how these number came up and how those lower two numbers impact relics are a bit of mystery.\nEspecially tentacle DMG is related to this, this is very important for Aequor players.\n\nAs far as I can tell, these number are not linear related to keeper's level, thanks to those who shared their numbers with me.\nSo the best we can do is to guess a approximate function....\n\nSince most game's description are kinda open, albeit sometimes confusing, but at least they are there. It's weird only this part is a black box.\n\nIf we have the formula, player can expect what kind of numbers they are gonna do.\nAnd it will be easier to build teams, write guides, give suggestions .etc\n\nAnd don't call me nerd, you are nerd!🥲", "timestamp": "2026-06-09T04:23:22.064000+00:00", "thread_id": "1513760393271443487", "attachments": [{"id": "1513760393875689652", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 908307, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1513760393271443487/1513760393875689652/image.png?ex=6a298f7a&is=6a283dfa&hm=9afac74ca20ae35763c65ce2321b1f6a1dcd0c41f98d4ee896accdb0c72e6708&"}]}
